<plot>News of U.S. presidential election results reverberated across continents. At the bottom of the world, the reaction of thousands of penguins to the promise of change is captured on film. A lighthearted, funny, whimsical look at election day in Antarctica, Penguins for Change also speaks to the changes global warming may have on this exquisitely beautiful land and its spirited inhabitants.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?428109</url></doc>
